<item>
            <title>[SPARK-12386] Setting &quot;spark.executor.port&quot; leads to NPE in SparkEnv</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-12386</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;From the list:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;when we set spark.executor.port in 1.6, we get thrown a NPE in SparkEnv$.create(SparkEnv.scala:259).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Fix is simple; probably should make it to 1.6.0 since it will affect anyone using that config options, but I&apos;ll leave that to the release manager&apos;s discretion.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12922543">SPARK-12386</key>
            <summary>Setting &quot;spark.executor.port&quot; leads to NPE in SparkEnv</summary>
